        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(auth): auto-correct type:token to type:api_key for Anthropic Enterprise API keys",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nWhen a user configures an Anthropic Enterprise API key with type: token (instead of type: api_key), the auth profile loader silently rejects it. The Enterprise API uses x-api-key header authentication — the same mechanism as standard API keys — so treating type: token as type: api_key is a safe auto-fix.\n\n## Changes\n\nsrc/agents/auth-profiles/persisted.ts: Add auto-correction mapping that converts type: token to type: api_key for Anthropic Enterprise API profiles.\n\n## Evidence\n\nAuth profile loading tests pass. The correction only affects Anthropic Enterprise profiles.\n\n**Label**: bug\n_AI-assisted._",
